mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.spatiotemporal
Class QueryViewInterpreter

java.lang.Object
  mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.FieldListener
      mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.ViewInterpreter
          mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.spatiotemporal.QueryViewInterpreter
public class QueryViewInterpreter
extends ViewInterpreter

QueryViewInterpreter is interested in the client's position and time as supplied by the query parameters. When the client moves signficantly or changes its time significantly, QueryViewInterpreter asks the authoritative State's Queryable to tell it what is no longer visible and what is newly visible.

Inputs from State: QueryFields.QUERYABLE_FIELDNAME

Query parameters (Inputs from client): QueryClientFields.POSITION_FIELDNAME, QueryClientFields.WIDTH_FIELDNAME, QueryClientFields.TIMELOWERBOUND_FIELDNAME, QueryClientFields.TIMEUPPERBOUND_FIELDNAME, QueryClientFields.FIELDS_FIELDNAME

Outputs to client: QueryFields.RESULTS_ADDED, QueryFields.RESULTS_REMOVED
